<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Job Recommendation</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #815931;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-right: auto; /* Push the brand to the left */
        }

        .navbar-nav {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar-nav li {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .navbar-nav li:first-child {
            margin-left: 0;
        }

        .navbar-nav li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative; /* Add relative position for loader */
        }
    
        /* Loader styles */
        .loader {
            position: relative;
            top: 28%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            display: none; /* Hide initially */
        }
    
        .loader img {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
        }
    
        h1 + p {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #302f2f;
        }
    
        h1 {
            text-align: center; 
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #815931;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-family: fantasy;
            font-style: italic;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
    
        h2 {
            text-align: center; 
            font-size: 2rem;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            color: #815931;
        }
    
        .card {
            background-color: #fff;
            background-image: url("https://st5.depositphotos.com/9999814/74746/i/450/depositphotos_747461576-stock-photo-human-resources-recruitment-people-networking.jpg");
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 70px auto;
            max-width: 1000px;
            height: 350px;
            position: relative;
        }
    
        .card-input {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background-color: rgba(235, 232, 232, 0.8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(91, 91, 91, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 400px;
            max-height: 200px;
            width: calc(100% - 80px);
            height: calc(100% - 80px);
        }
    
        label {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    
        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
    
        button[type="submit"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #815931;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    
        button[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #6f4a28;
        }
    
        .description {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
    
        .recommendation-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    
        .recommendation-card {
            width: calc(50% - 20px);
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-height: 200px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
    
        .recommendation-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
    
        .recommendation-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #815931;
        }
    
        .recommendation-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
    
        /* Footer styles */
        .footer {
            background-color: #815931;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 10px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    
        .footer a {
            color: #ffd700; /* Golden color for links */
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
    
    
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-brand">CAREER CATALYST</div>
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Don't be pushed around by the fears in your mind.<br>Be led by the dreams in your heart.</h1>
        <p>Explore Your Interests: Begin your career journey by exploring your interests, hobbies, and passions.<br>Consider what activities bring you joy and fulfillment. Your interests can provide valuable insights into potential career paths.</p>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-input">
                <form id="job-finder" action="/career" method="post">
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <label for="c_education">Education</label>
                        <input type="text" id="c_education" name="c_education" required><br>
                        <label for="Details">Interests</label>
                        <input type="text" id="Details" name="Details" required><br>
                        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Your Exclusive Suggestions</h2>
        <% if (locals.result) { %>
            <div class="textbox-container">
                <%- include('careerinfo.ejs') %>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Career Catalyst. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
